{
  "stem": "25639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the plums, for example, would be turned into jams-- wonderful jams.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a huge copper kettle, which also went from farm to farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We owned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a very interesting story behind it, but first allow me to tell you what we did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a 24-hour process to cook in this huge kettle all the plums.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a big party, and the relatives and friends were invited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, the inside of this huge, huge kettle was an agitator with a long handle, and a special side wall was built around it so that it would not move.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they let it dry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and there was a fire under it, a very slow fire, and it had to be constantly stirred.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was really fun, and we would sing and have a party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I always looked forward to this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a harvest party, around Sukkot, around the time of the harvesting period.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when the Hungarians came in, they began to collect copper kettles and pots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they went from house to house, in the name of the Hungarian government, and collected all copper utensils, as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they took our kettle, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the whole town missed it, because there were, I think, only a couple of them in the entire town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After that, we just had to use pots that-- pots that were not suitable for this purpose.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First of all, it was not big enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Life there was really friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We lived together with non-Jewish neighbors and all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was no Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We lived together with every type of person, except for the Gypsies.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
